Javier Mascherano has posted a photo online demonstrating the less glamorous side of international football.

The Barcelona midfielder uploaded the snap to his Twitter account which showed him and Sergio Aguero looking bored while Lionel Messi, Gonzalo Higuain, Angel di Maria, Lucas Biglia and others sat around playing cards.

Mascherano wrote: 'Bored with @aguerosergiokun while they play cards...' 

